íŔ@46499d5428f06d939bc932bb02dc1975f30e4a6a45574bcc77d884ccb93cfb87ŕČTitle: title: str trim
Path: Examples
Content:
Trim whitespace.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'Nu shell ' | str trim
Nu shell

```
Trim a specific character (not the whitespace).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '=== Nu shell ===' | str trim --char '='
 Nu shell

```
Trim whitespace from the beginning of string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ' Nu shell ' | str trim --left
Nu shell

```
Trim whitespace from the end of string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ' Nu shell ' | str trim --right
 Nu shell

```
Trim a specific character only from the end of the string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '=== Nu shell ===' | str trim --right --char '='
=== Nu shell

```
